                <ul class="check-list">
                    <li><i class="fa-solid fa-heart"></i> We don't shame you</li>
                    <li><i class="fa-solid fa-heart"></i> We don't break your streak</li>
                    <li><i class="fa-solid fa-heart"></i> We don't send notifications that make you feel worse</li>
                </ul>
                <p>Go back and log whenever you're ready. Or take the time you need. We understand.</p>
                <blockquote>"Your worst day is when tracking matters most. So we made sure it works even then."</blockquote>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- MEET LALAH -->
