                        <li><i class="fa-solid fa-check"></i> No guilt when you forget</li>
                        <li><i class="fa-solid fa-check"></i> Data never lost</li>
                        <li><i class="fa-solid fa-check"></i> No setup required</li>
                    </ul>
                    <p class="tagline">All the pretty, none of the pressure. <i class="fa-solid fa-heart"></i></p>
